title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 52)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Continuing along, here is another batch of music previously made available on Christian Tunes.  If you were able to download any of these albums earlier this month, and have some free bandwidth to spare today, I'd appreciate the seeding help.  If you're unsure how, simply (1) create a folder called "2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 52)" in the same folder where your torrents are usually downloaded to.  (2) copy and paste your downloaded music into that folder.  (3) then download the torrent as you normally would.  Your torrent client will recognize that you already have some of these albums, and instead of a downloader, you will be recognized as an uploader for those albums you just copied over.

Following this torrent today, I still have 92 additional 2014 titles to share from the previous month.  Hopefully I'll be able to get to those in short order.  In the mean while, I continue to work towards creating a new torrent with fresh music which I also hope to share with everyone soon.
